<a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-c%E1%BB%95-ca/poem-SQLcZneUoty6Zn7UCfgM4Q">Thạch cổ ca - 石鼓歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thi%C3%AAn-D%E1%BB%A5c-phi%C3%AAu-k%E1%BB%B5-ca/poem-4H7cidyLDPJCsh696qWFuQ">Thiên Dục phiêu kỵ ca - 天育驃騎歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/Xu%C3%A2n-du-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-eEt5sYUexjOxHUesi0jRKw">Xuân du khúc kỳ 2 - 春遊曲其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/author-RmmfVoamdwhG77VOgdRDUQ">Trương Trọng Tố</a>)<br></div>	</div>
